### 1. Root Endpoint
GET http://localhost:5000/

### 2. Dashboard Summary (All Roles)
# Returns income/expense, balance, breakdown, and 6-month monthly trends.
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/summary
x-user-id: 642e12e3a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8  # Replace with actual Seeder Admin ID

### 3. Financial Records - List (Analyst/Admin)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/records
x-user-id: 642e12e3a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b9

### 4. Financial Records - With Search (Analyst/Admin)
# Keywords filter descriptions and categories.
GET http://localhost:5000/api/records?search=Salary
x-user-id: 642e12e3a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b9

### 5. Financial Records - With Pagination (Analyst/Admin)
# Parameters: page=1, limit=5
GET http://localhost:5000/api/records?page=1&limit=2
x-user-id: 642e12e3a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b9

### 6. Create Record (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/records
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: 642e12e3a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8

{
  "amount": 2500,
  "type": "income",
  "category": "Project",
  "description": "New website design payment"
}

### 7. Soft Delete Record (Admin Only)
# Change the ID to an existing record ID.
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/records/RECORD_ID_HERE
x-user-id: 642e12e3a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8

### 8. Unauthorized Access Test (Viewer trying to create record)
# Expected: 403 Forbidden
POST http://localhost:5000/api/records
Content-Type: application/json
x-user-id: 642e12e3a1b2c3d4e5f6a7ba  # Replace with actual Viewer ID

{
  "amount": 100,
  "type": "expense",
  "category": "Coffee",
  "description": "Starbucks"
}

### 9. Inactive User Test (Any request with inactive user)
# Expected: 403 Forbidden - Access denied.
# (Update status of a user to inactive to test)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard/summary
x-user-id: 642e12e3a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8
